cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as relation extraction and utilizes word embeddings. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new model that combines both hand-crafted features and learned word embeddings. Additionally, it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with a task that requires understanding and processing of natural language. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it utilizes neural networks for relation extraction. Finally, it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as relation extraction is a common task in information retrieval.
